now the computer gives video but with a white screen, activitie usb.Not video external.sometimes  fan restarts constantly and it doesn't turn on.where would the problem be? in this moment computer doesn't turn on only fan restarts constantly

Did you mean 2936, instead of 2836?

Check R7402...
ALL_SYS_PWRGD  goes up and down to 3v as the fan restarts
yes, the problem persists, Veo que la placa tiene un poco de oxido en general, en los test point.Crees que un lavado ultrasonico pueda solucionar problema?

In such case, reball SMC first.
Any pulse at VCORE?
Just in case, remove Q7950.
